Package org.universAAL.ri.gateway.proxies.exporting

Exporting Proxies, are those components that represent local components inside the Gateway, and handle the operations required in other for remote Space to communicate with them.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProxyContextPublisher
    A ContextPublisher which will listen to remote ProxyContextSubscriber' messages and reinject them in to the local bus.
    ProxySCaller
    Proxy that receives ServiceCalls and injects them to the bus in other to get a ServiceResponse from the represented ServiceCallee.
